{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place butter into mixing bowl and melt <b>2 min\/70°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add milk, eggs, sugar, plain flour, baking powder and salt and mix <b>10 sec\/speed 5<b>.","To cook pancakes, heat ½-1 tsp butter in a frying pan over medium heat. For each pancake, pour in a ladle of batter and cook 1-2 minutes or until bubbles start bursting on pancake surface. Turn pancake over and cook for a further 1 minute. Transfer into a ThermoServer or onto a plate and cover with kitchen towel to keep warm. Repeat with remaining batter. Serve hot."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["50 g butter, plus extra for frying","300 g milk","2 eggs","30 g sugar","200 g plain flour","1 tbsp baking powder","¼ tsp salt"]}],"id":"r66932","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-kLZM44iXdXs\/XZafoKriZTI\/AAAAAAAAgwU\/j-eo_9A1iOMmPwxqTyfD_21fH1BTtFbxQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_sYssTScrYRAljbMZ.png","title":"American-style pancakes","publishedAt":"2014-09-05T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"4 g","fat":"6 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"16 g","calories":"548 kJ \/ 131 kcal"},"usefulItems":"ladle, turner \/ fish slice, ThermoServer, kitchen towel, frying pan, stove","hintsAndTricks":["To substitute butter with oil, omit step 1 and add 50 g oil along with all other ingredients in step 2. Use oil instead of butter for frying.","Serve pancakes with maple syrup, whipped cream, chocolate, caramel or jam.","<strong>Blueberry <\/strong>or <strong>raspberry pancakes<\/strong>: scatter 1 tbsp berries onto each pancake right after pouring batter into frying pan, before bubbles start to form.","<strong>Chocolate pancakes<\/strong>: add 2 tsp cocoa powder in step 2."],"basicInfo":["easy","40m","40m","12 pieces"]}